issue.title: Issue with Finding Ignition Protobuf Messages

content.raw:
I was get around my protobuf issues and compile the subt tunnel circuit branch by: 

1. Installing protobuf to /usr instead of its default /usr/local  
2. Deleting some old protobuf cmake files that were trying to find protobuf in the wrong directories.  These cmake files were in /usr/local/lib/cmake/protobuf.  I’m not sure where these files came from, but perhaps they were left by an older version of the gazebo packages.
content.html:
I was get around my protobuf issues and compile the subt tunnel circuit branch by:

  1. Installing protobuf to /usr instead of its default /usr/local
  2. Deleting some old protobuf cmake files that were trying to find protobuf in the wrong directories. These cmake files were in /usr/local/lib/cmake/protobuf. I’m not sure where these files came from, but perhaps they were left by an older version of the gazebo packages.
